    "It could also be used for reformulating goals in the correct terms, before they will be transformed into more powerful AGI, like adding context, time and place constrains etc.",
    "Gatekeeper AI may decline to proceed with unbounded, aggressive, black-listed, or not-white-listed goals.",
    "It could ask to reformulate the same goal in other words before it will go to the main AI.",
    "It could ask additional questions for the goal verification.",
    "Gatekeeper AI should be a Narrow AI with a rather simple reasoning, maybe a combination of neural net and rule-based AI, so there will be no need to ensure its safety too."
